bill.title: OGSR/Identification of a Minor [SPSC]
bill.description: Amends specified provision relating to a public records exemption for information contained in court files which identifies a minor petitioning for a waiver of the notice requirements contained in the Parental Notice of Abortion Act. Saves the exemption from repeal under the OGSR Act, etc.
